{
  "text": "I was guessing that the crossed legs of the SDN card form had a meaning similar to the cross of the crux on side. Is this correct? I am this is correct. The cross formed by the living limbs of the image signifies that which is the innature of mind, body, spirit, complexes in manifestation within your illusion. There is no experience which is not purchased by effort of a sum kind, no act of service to self or others, which does not bear a price to the entity manifesting, commensurate with its purity. All things in a manifestation may be seen in one way or another to be offering themselves in order that transformations may take place upon the level appropriate to the action.",
